RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: EXISTS (SELECT * FROM LBTBS_PRAM_MSG_REGEN WHERE PRAM_SOURCE_REF_NO = CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND MODULE_CODE='LB' AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM smvws_user_branches b WHERE b.user_id = global.user_id AND b.Branch_code = oltb_contract.branch)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO,B.PRAM_SOURCE_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A , LBTBS_PRAM_MSG_REGEN B WHERE B.PRAM_SOURCE_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO
